{"tid":2215873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大BMO撤出香港ETF市場","createTime":"2020-09-24T09:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:48:21.000Z","uid":225931,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e05e41fd14b96edd98f11af3fa7faefcb212eb1","tid":2215873,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:34:16.000Z","msg":"繼領航投資（Vanguard）撤出香港交易所買賣基金（ETF）市場後，外電報道，加拿大BMO環球資產管理亦計劃退出香港ETF市場，並將旗下7隻ETF交由華夏基金（香港）接手，目前正確認有關轉移條款。BMO環球資產管理及華夏基金（香港）均不予置評。<br />\n<br />\nBMO於2014年進軍香港，在港有7隻ETF，合共資產總值只有約28.6億元，其中最大的ETF為BMO亞洲美元投資級別債券ETF  ，資產規模約17億元；最小的ETF為BMO MSCI亞太區房地產ETF資產規模只有約840萬元。<br />\n<br />\nBMO旗下ETF交投十分疏落，03141周三的交投只有約31萬元。報道指，BMO互惠基金（Mutual Fund）業務及BMO銀行在港的私人銀行服務則不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n現時本港ETF供應商近30家，只有6家的本地ETF資產超過10億元，當中包括道富環球、恒生投資管理、貝萊德、南方東英等。"},{"pid":"fc13904b0fa285f24f49a4c7785be639f0aaf1b1","tid":2215873,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8de45ad5984d0d6e9319336487a1f5ad3d3bd0","tid":2215873,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"【最強文宣！】「新疆數據計畫」上線！一站式提供有關新疆受壓迫民族嘅資料<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2215872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2215872</a>"},{"pid":"ed1ed47335d6d93e5d2483bb112d54fd8f8fcdd8","tid":2215873,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:45:35.000Z","msg":"各位股民睇路"},{"pid":"ac0773c1bef6c334f3b4debd42fbae158433f41e","tid":2215873,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:46:39.000Z","msg":"金融中心內循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c150c05020b3678e1adc014d857463d6392d6ec","tid":2215873,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"進軍澳門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 